    RIDESIDE.NET

%div
  Powered by <a href="http://tumblr.com">tumblr.com</a> (<< click there to post).

%div{:class=>"content"}
  - @posts.each do |p|
    %hr
    %div{:class=>"post"}
      %a{:href=>"#{p['blog_name']}.tumblr.com"}
        = p['blog_name']
      = p['date']
      %a{:href=>"#{p['post_url']}"}
        >>
      %div{:class=>"post-content"}
        %strong
          = p['title']
        = p['description']
        = p['body']
         
      
